oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The Dairy Industry at the Turn of the Century
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Novakovic, Andrew
Jack, Kevin
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: dairy industry
21st Century
factors
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Numerous factors have shaped the dairy industry in the past. Many of these same factors continue, in one form or another, to affect it today. Some new factors are exerting new influences. This paper attempts to discuss factors that may be important in shaping the dairy sector as we approach the 21st Century.
